snippet.textDisplay: I am a great fan of Star Wars. Yesterday we were engaged and busy with our side hustle. Suddenly, this exotic Coke song Turri Jani started playing on our screen, which enraptured our attention, though I don't listen much to songs. But it left me with a big Wow, to see the entire setup of this beautiful song, made me jump into the world of a Star Wars, small town. Appreciate this amazing concept.  It's just super to explore we already have hidden talented Directors and producers. like George Lucas in Pakistan now. I don't know how many of you are Star Wars fans here who have these same vibes hovering in my mind.
